Somehow he still has his job. Also got caught cheating on his wife with her best friend for three years. Would have been twice divorced before turning 39, but sadly his wife died a month ago. Such a disaster, and seeing this beautiful performance had me in tears thinking about my “wife” worst year of my life, but this performance was absolutely stunning and atleast made me feel moved for the first time in months.
